    'description' => 'Download images and binary files from URLs to the workspace with automatic format detection via magic bytes (file signatures), content-based naming, and integrity verification. Supports JPEG, PNG, GIF, WEBP, BMP, SVG, ICO, and generic binaries. Uses PHP streams with timeouts, validates file size limits, and detects MIME type from both Content-Type header and actual file content. Composes with image_info for metadata extraction. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
